message.body: What happened to my baby?
Daaaaaaaarling!!!! Your fiancé is waaaaaaaiting!!!!
Im sorry baby!!!!! Im just getting out now. Yucky work :-/
Oh no!!! Hurry back! I save you!
I hurry i hurry!!! Hope youre ok, darling!
At the back of the bus!
Like the way way back!? Be comfy!
Three rows from the back :D
Good thing I had that advil!
:) Not so bad! Have a nice bus ride darling!! Talk to you later. Youre
gonna have to tell me allll about your first minutes home haha

No. Not so bad. Thank you very much for this week! It has certainly been the absolute best birthday ever! I cannot even begin to tell you. Can't wait for forever!!!!! I love you so much, my wonderful fiancé!
And I don't think there will be too much to tell :)
I'm sitting under this light and can I tell you....my ring SPARKLES!
Ahahah stop staring at it you cutie!! And, my love, i am so so so very happy, and i thank you for every single smile
It is not hard to smile when I'm with you! And I will not!!!! I finally get to stare at it in all its glory without you looking at me. Hah
Hahah oooh i was not judging!!! Im so happy!
Oh good!!! There's gonna be more smiles!
Haha double good! Love the smiles haha. Love you!!!
I love you too! So much!
:) ! Settle in a be a happy lady, my love!
Will do!!! I'll call you later!
Please do!
Even in the dark my ring sparkles :D
Bayyyyybeeee!
